snippet.title: Roboholic — Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Play the demo and wishlist on Steam → https://bit.ly/RoboholicReveal
Roboholic is a roguelite FPS with wacky physics and even wackier abilities. Play as an ex-farmer turned robot who is resurrected over and over again to defeat a crazed warlord, while fighting an army of genetically modified soldiers and malfunctioning droids.
